      • isActive

        public boolean isActive​(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
        Return true if this tab should be active / selected in the global UI.

        Only checks http parameter is set.

        AbstractPropertyUI.isEnabled() is not checked here.

        Default is false.

        Parameters:
        request - the request to read parameter from
        Returns:
        active state of tab
        See Also:
        getParamName()
